《'''Lean On'''》是一首由音樂團體{{le|超級雷射光|Major Lazer}}與[[DJ_Snake|DJ Snake]]共同製作的一首[[電子音樂|電子音樂]][[舞曲|舞曲]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://zumic.com/music-videos/159598/lean-on-major-lazer-dj-snake-ft-mo-youtube-official-lyric-video-lyrics/|title="Lean On" - Major Lazer & DJ Snake ft MØ [YouTube Official Lyric Video + Lyrics] - Zumic - Free Music, Lyrics, Reviews|author=Chris Tart|work=Zumic|accessdate=2016-03-12|archive-date=2017-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824211359/https://zumic.com/music-videos/159598/lean-on-major-lazer-dj-snake-ft-mo-youtube-official-lyric-video-lyrics/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.brightsidelive.com/major-lazer-dj-snake-ft-mo-release-lean/|title=Major Lazer and DJ Snake ft. MØ release "Lean On"|work=Brightside|access-date=2016-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150307003941/http://www.brightsidelive.com/major-lazer-dj-snake-ft-mo-release-lean/|archive-date=2015-03-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，收錄於2015年的錄音室專輯《[[和平任務|和平任務]]》（''Peace Is the Mission''），人聲及填詞則與歌手[[MØ|MØ]]合作<ref>{{cite web|title=BMI Repertoire - Lean On|url=http://repertoire.bmi.com/title.asp?blnWriter=True&blnPublisher=True&blnArtist=True&keyID=19291520&ShowNbr=0&ShowSeqNbr=0&querytype=WorkID|website=bmi.com|accessdate=2015-07-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150718215357/http://repertoire.bmi.com/title.asp?blnWriter=True&blnPublisher=True&blnArtist=True&keyID=19291520&ShowNbr=0&ShowSeqNbr=0&querytype=WorkID|archivedate=2015-07-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Dolan|first=Jon|date=2015-06-02|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/major-lazer-peace-is-the-mission-20150602|title=Major Lazer's New Album: Peace Is the Mission|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|publisher=[[Jann_Wenner|Wenner Media]]|accessdate=2015-06-06|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612143451/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/major-lazer-peace-is-the-mission-20150602|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.idolator.com/7597016/major-lazer-dj-snake-mo-lean-on-song-summer|title=Will Major Lazer, DJ Snake & MØ’s "Lean On" Be 2015's Song of the Summer?|publisher=Idolator.com}}</ref>。這首歌作為專輯的先行單曲於2015年3月2日獨立發行<ref name="iTunes">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/it/album/lean-on-feat.-m-dj-snake-single/id970116761|title=Lean On (feat. MØ and DJ Snake) - Single di Major Lazer|language=it|publisher=[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]] (IT)|accessdate=2015-06-11|archive-date=2015-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701131026/https://itunes.apple.com/it/album/lean-on-feat.-m-dj-snake-single/id970116761|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《Lean On》取得了評論及商業上的成功，在多個國家來到單曲周榜一位及年榜前十位的成績。2015年11月，《Lean On》成為[[spotify|spotify]]創立以來串流數最高的歌曲，於全球累積5億2千6百萬次串流，並且持續增加中<ref name="most streamed">{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/nov/12/spotify-most-streamed-track-all-time-major-lazer-lean-on|title=Leaning power: Spotify names its most streamed track of all time|date=2015-11-12|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]]|accessdate=2015-11-12|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114021705/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/nov/12/spotify-most-streamed-track-all-time-major-lazer-lean-on|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]在[[印度|印度]]多個地區及瑞典的[[斯德哥爾摩市政廳|斯德哥爾摩市政廳]]拍攝，於2015年3月23日上傳[[YouTube|YouTube]]。截至2019年1月17日，已經累積超過24億次點閱。

